ğŸ¯ â­ Short Story (Exam Style)

ğŸ‘‰ When sending a WhatsApp message, the Application layer creates the message, 
Presentation encrypts it, Session manages the chat connection, Transport segments 
data using TCP, Network adds IP for routing, Data Link adds MAC for local delivery, 
and Physical transmits bits over the network.



Task 3 : TCP/IP Model 
Application Layer: The OSI model application, presentation and session layers, i.e., layers 5, 6, and 7, are grouped into the application layer in the TCP/IP model.
Transport Layer: This is layer 4.
Internet Layer: This is layer 3. The OSI modelâ€™s network layer is called the Internet layer in the TCP/IP model.
Link Layer: This is layer 2.



